#### Issue details

Hey, im trying to implement a list that is refreshed once the datamodell changes.
Im useing a Vertical Group for this, cause i need to add and remove items.
indexOutOfBoundsException happens randomly, im not sure why.
#### Reproduction steps/code

The propertyChange method is called each time something on the datamodel changes.
The crash happens like randomly, sometimes it works and suddenly it crashes.

